import { Box } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import RouterPath from '../../Routes/RouterPath'

import Footer from './Footer'
import Header from './Header'


const Layout = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Header />
     
        <Box sx={{ my: 20, height:'100vh'}}>
    
        <RouterPath />
        </Box>
      <Footer />
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Layout
